REM Formula found by SHELXT: C7 N7 Br8 Pb2
CELL 0.71073 41.6845 23.962 12.0004 90 90 90
ZERR 32 0.0083 0.0048 0.0024 0 0 0
LATT -5
SYMM -X,-Y,+Z
SYMM 0.5+X,0.5-Y,+Z
SYMM 0.5-X,0.5+Y,+Z
SFAC C H Br N Pb
UNIT 192 576 128 64 32
DFIX 1.5 C1 C2
